            "title": "12 Health Care Stocks Moving In Friday&#39;s After-Market Session",
            "description": "<div><div class=\"sc-fLvBnq jggrSb\"><!--$--><h3 class=\"block core-block\">Gainers</h3><!--/$--><!--$--><ul class=\"block core-block\">\n<li><strong>Pheton Holdings</strong> <span class=\"ticker\" data-exchange=\"NASDAQ\" data-ticker=\"PTHL\" style=\"display:inline-block\">PTHL</span> shares rose 8.2% to $14.61 during Friday's after-market session. The market value of their outstanding shares is at $211.8 million. </li>\n<li><strong>Nuwellis</strong> <span class=\"ticker\" data-exchange=\"NASDAQ\" data-ticker=\"NUWE\" style=\"display:inline-block\">NUWE</span> shares rose 6.67% to $0.43. The company's market cap stands at $1.8 million. </li>\n<li><strong>Alaunos Therapeutics</strong> <span class=\"ticker\" data-exchange=\"NASDAQ\" data-ticker=\"TCRT\" style=\"display:inline-block\">TCRT</span> stock rose 6.66% to $3.2. The market value of their outstanding shares is at $5.2 million. </li>\n<li><strong>ABVC BioPharma</strong> <span class=\"ticker\" data-exchange=\"NASDAQ\" data-ticker=\"ABVC\" style=\"display:inline-block\">ABVC</span> stock rose 6.38% to $1.64. The market value of their outstanding shares is at $27.8 million. </li>\n<li><strong>Jupiter Neurosciences</strong> <span class=\"ticker\" data-exchange=\"NASDAQ\" data-ticker=\"JUNS\" style=\"display:inline-block\">JUNS</span> shares increased by 6.25% to $0.82. The company's market cap stands at $27.1 million. </li>\n<li><strong>Femasys</strong> <span class=\"ticker\" data-exchange=\"NASDAQ\" data-ticker=\"FEMY\" style=\"display:inline-block\">FEMY</span> stock rose 6.24% to $0.85. The market value of their outstanding shares is at $23.1 million. </li>\n</ul><!--/$--><!--$--><h3 class=\"block core-block\">Losers</h3><!--/$--><!--$--><!--/$--><!--$--><!--$--><div class=\"sc-exeBjx kjPTmb raptive-ad-placement mx-auto overflow-hidden min-h-[250px] min-w-[300px] raptive-ad-wrapper flex flex-col items-center justify-center\"><div class=\"raptive-ben-content w-full flex items-center j